S --> NP VP
VP --> VP PP
VP --> TVerb NP
VP --> DTVerb NP PP
VP --> DTVerb NP NP
VP --> VP
VP --> IVerb

VP --> TVerb that S


NP --> Det Noun
NP --> Pat | Robin
NP --> NP PP

PP --> Prep NP
PP --> NP Post

Det --> the | a | an
Prep --> to | on | with
Post --> ago


Noun --> book | car | roses | telescope | pirates
TVerb --> saw 
DTVerb --> gave | put
